{"tid":455112,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解要到我終於放棄, 你先識著緊我","createTime":"2017-11-01T20:08:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-02T09:00:06.000Z","uid":135284,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"98e9e6583de61b9eab0cca8e28ec3292fa914141","tid":455112,"uid":135284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T20:08:21.000Z","msg":"其實我仲鍾意你 我仲等緊你個解釋<br />\n等緊你同我講 : 我個心宜家只有你一個<br />\n自從同你講我地做返朋友 你先開始緊張我<br />\n先識驚以後會真係冇咗我 驚我永遠離開你 先識挽留我<br />\n但係個陣我係你女朋友嘅時候 你就唔嗲唔吊<br />\n當我可有可無 佢唔理你 你先理下我<br />\n點解你咁犯賤 點解我咁犯賤<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e396fddb2ff02fd123d40de151bcdba63c00f061","tid":455112,"uid":139487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T20:11:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab685e115749ac8b63e3a6ce7a929376331c917d","tid":455112,"uid":12696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T20:59:57.000Z","msg":"人就係咁犯賤<br />\n如果我可以有多次機會同佢一齊<br />\n我一定會好好珍惜佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b73e9cc60fdb2b7809730fdc45e9bdfe6c7e962c","tid":455112,"uid":41509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T21:10:50.000Z","msg":"你幾大?<br />\n戀呢家野,失多兩次,痛多兩次就慣"},{"pid":"544c08c4f4f1a708c4921ec133bcab2c27a99294","tid":455112,"uid":137369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:48:18.000Z","msg":"揾翻佢啦 佢會對你更好"},{"pid":"ca163ddef1089af452c7c46963505ba1d7a1673b","tid":455112,"uid":140234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T09:00:06.000Z","msg":"你諗多左啦 係分左手冇地方出火先搵返你"}]}